title: Sami Yusuf - Al Mu allim (320kbs)  [akhiugo]
description:
As salaam alaikum wa rahmatuallahi wa barakatuh,

Al-Mu'allim is a compilation of some ground breaking nasheeds, mostly in English, by Sami Yusuf. Al-Mu'allim or beloved teacher is an album praising the beloved Prophet Muhammad (saw) who was the best of teachers of all time. Prophet Muhammad (saw) is never far from our minds and this album is to bring us even closer to his teachings by way of reminder and inspiration.


1. Al-Mu Allim
2. Who Is the Loved One
3. The Cave of Hira
4. Allahu
5. The Creator
6. Meditation
7. Ya Mustafa
8. Supplication
